==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Converter
<hw>Con*vert"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who converts; one who makes converts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Steel Manuf.)</fld> <def>A retort, used in the
Bessemer process, in which molten cast iron is decarburized and
converted into steel by a blast of air forced through the liquid
metal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Convertibility</ent>⟦br⟧
